  <brief_title>Effect of Short-term Oxygen During CPET in COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Short-term Oxygen Therapy on Cardiopulmonary Exercise (CPET) Capacity in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</official_title>
