  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease

          -  on optimized medical therapy and in stable condition for at least 4 week

          -  desaturate in the 6 minute walking test by at least 4% to values &lt;92%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  unstable conditions

          -  pregnant women

          -  patients with relevant concomitant lung disease and severe daytime hypoxemia
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
